  "title": "QUANTITY SURVEYOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>QUANTITY SURVEYORS (Jnr &amp; Snr position)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>(Project)</strong></p>\n<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Taking off quantities for tendering.</li>\n  <li>Pricing of bills &amp; quantities.</li>\n  <li>Evaluation of sub-contractor’s claims &amp; preparation of payment certificate for sub-contractors.</li>\n  <li>Sourcing &amp; purchasing of construction materials, equipment etc.</li>\n  <li>Sourcing &amp; Coordination of new subcontractors &amp; suppliers.</li>\n  <li>Contract administration including preparation of variation claims &amp; progress claims.</li>\n  <li>Any other duties assigned by Superior or Management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Recognized Degree / Diploma in Civil &amp; Structural or Mechanical &amp; Electrical Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years or more <strong>relevant work experiences in Singapore Construction sector</strong>; 8 years &amp; above if apply for Senior or Managerial      position.</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates or those without experience may apply</li>\n  <li>Salary will be commensurate in accordance with work experience and qualifications etc</li>\n  <li>Only Singapore/SPR need apply</li>\n</ul>",
